{
  "text": "where the constraint basically restricts the noise by \u2264 \u03b5. DS uses the \u221e norm penalty to denoise X T \u221e \u2264 \u03bb as shown above. LASSO applies the same spirit as DS [CITATION_1] ] to denoise, but uses a different formulation\u03b2",
